    {
      "para_id": "Q001818.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Šara , the confidant of An , the beloved child of Inana , his master , Šu-Suen , the beloved of Enlil , the king whom Enlil chose with the love of his heart , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , built the E-šage-pada , his beloved temple ."
    }
  ],
